  "851800": {
    "name": "G2 Fighter / 基因特工",
    "steam_appid": 851800,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/b31cd20fa3566a1d1db75232c4ac06af.poster.avif?t=1708687300\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/b31cd20fa3566a1d1db75232c4ac06af.webm?t=1708687300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/b31cd20fa3566a1d1db75232c4ac06af.mp4?t=1708687300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>基因特工是一款Low Poly风格的Top-Down视角射击RPG。我们创造了一个宏大的世界版图，搭建了各式各样的城市和场景，玩家在这个世界中自由自在地战斗、驾驶、创造并完成各种任务。大家可以跟随我们的主角“伯恩-皮耶龙”一起去亲历这个混乱纷杂的末日世界，共同探秘旧人类世界灭亡的真相，彻查故事幕后的黑手。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重要通知</h2>万分抱歉，由于新版本添加了金色装备和立绘图鉴等新功能，游戏的数据结构发生了改变，导致此次新版本上线后，玩家的游戏记录将被重置。但诸位特工可以重启征程，体验全新的游戏内容。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/074ddad89c0c2989b9b9db90c597801a.avif?t=1708687300\" width=626 height=123 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >爽快的战斗</h2>你最多可以携带三种远程武器，一种近战武器，一种手雷以及多个技能。强大的火力配置将帮助大家在万军从中杀出一条血路，无双的战斗体验，变态的地狱难度，将会令你欲罢不能。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/b86a491c7d250e3db5c52e3aa3fa522a.poster.avif?t=1708687300\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/b86a491c7d250e3db5c52e3aa3fa522a.webm?t=1708687300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/b86a491c7d250e3db5c52e3aa3fa522a.mp4?t=1708687300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样的装备</h2>随机掉落的装备有着不同质量和品级，还可以通过强化和镶嵌特殊配件让装备属性得到二次提升。在这里你可以利用不同的属性组合去造就大量独一无二的装备，后期“刷神装”的成就感也将给予玩家更多乐趣。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/9c0cf40b56ce6fcbd2eab77247df315a.poster.avif?t=1708687300\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/9c0cf40b56ce6fcbd2eab77247df315a.webm?t=1708687300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/9c0cf40b56ce6fcbd2eab77247df315a.mp4?t=1708687300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的任务</h2>除了主线流程之外，游戏中还有大量可供你选择的支线任务，剧情走向会因任务的选择而变化，部分任务会因为互斥的原因在游戏进程中关闭。在主线进度达到一定阶段后，玩家将能够无视任务，开启“刷刷刷”的副本玩法。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/4c2d12d178d5755f7062fb2007275f24.poster.avif?t=1708687300\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/4c2d12d178d5755f7062fb2007275f24.webm?t=1708687300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/4c2d12d178d5755f7062fb2007275f24.mp4?t=1708687300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自由的世界</h2>实时流动的时间除了光影效果外，还会影响各种事件的触发和任务完成情况；开放式的大地图则任由你在广袤的大地上驰骋，随着剧情的推进，会解锁更多游戏区域；游戏中的不同势力（新人类，旧人类，变异体，机器人等）之间的关系也将随着故事的进行而改变。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/c6bf775adb8822aa50f16fdcafdc5baa.poster.avif?t=1708687300\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/c6bf775adb8822aa50f16fdcafdc5baa.webm?t=1708687300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/c6bf775adb8822aa50f16fdcafdc5baa.mp4?t=1708687300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >生动的配音</h2>我们邀请到了Doug Cockle等十余位经验丰富的配音演员前往伦敦的OMUK工作室进行了游戏的英文配音工作。原声语音赋予角色鲜活的生命力，使故事更加立体，让你沉浸在基因特工的世界中。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/ad98db01b91d32031670b37e0db6da01.poster.avif?t=1708687300\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/ad98db01b91d32031670b37e0db6da01.webm?t=1708687300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/ad98db01b91d32031670b37e0db6da01.mp4?t=1708687300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢快的联机</h2>精心打造的联机模式让《G2 Fighter》不再只是一款单机游戏，多人联机的体验将超乎以往，队友间的掩护，突进，火力支援，技能搭配和战术安排都将使战局千变万化，你可以搭档默契的好友，一起面对更艰难的挑战，亦或是与好友互坑，度过一段开心的时光。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/24842c0c4b9378565977a2e05407128c.poster.avif?t=1708687300\" width=640 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/24842c0c4b9378565977a2e05407128c.webm?t=1708687300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/24842c0c4b9378565977a2e05407128c.mp4?t=1708687300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>由于某些原因，游戏联机部分的服务器设立在海外，可能会发生网络连接不稳定的情况。目前国内服务器的手续也在加紧申请中。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >注意！</h2>如出现上述情况，请参考以下几点：<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>加群326466549，在群文件中下载小黑盒加速器，登录并加速游戏<br></li><li>请不要挂任何加速器或VPN，直接裸连<br></li><li>请尝试修改DNS为固定值（腾讯或阿里）<br></li><li>组队游戏时，即便掉线，也能重新加入到之前的房间，你没有拾取的装备会在基地等着你</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/5250025a3d61dda1ecac6a784176b9ce.avif?t=1708687300\" width=626 height=123 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开发计划</h2><br>我们计划在未来的时间中持续完善游戏的各部分内容，以下新内容将在之后陆续发布<br>* 故事主线第三章开启，搭建模式第一阶段（城市搭建基础功能）<br>* 故事主线第三章上线，搭建模式第二阶段（城市资源物资获取）<br>* 故事主线第四章（含多种副本玩法）上线，格斗系统模块优化（迭代优化基础战斗木块的城支行系统）<br>* 故事主线第五章上线，主线完毕，实力军团战斗模板实装<br>* Nintendo Switch和其他Console平台的移植工作同步进行，预计明年发布<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/7a5c492f8c1739f47eb3fa98c1e29de1.poster.avif?t=1708687300\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/7a5c492f8c1739f47eb3fa98c1e29de1.webm?t=1708687300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/851800/extras/7a5c492f8c1739f47eb3fa98c1e29de1.mp4?t=1708687300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
